  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2478430/extras/4daed031f0401d492d70f9585bcc456b.avif?t=1713954052\" width=660 height=141 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2478430/extras/6e0b1009c941e1da91a18b0932e16da4.poster.avif?t=1713954052\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2478430/extras/6e0b1009c941e1da91a18b0932e16da4.webm?t=1713954052\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2478430/extras/6e0b1009c941e1da91a18b0932e16da4.mp4?t=1713954052\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>The aliens arrived and they are not friendly at all.<br><br>The last hope for the mankind is a Kiwi<br><br>He, with the help of his jetpack, is the only one who can counteract the aliens and their army with devastating weapons.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2478430/extras/24a814772cfd4c20d0e526867d920f75.poster.avif?t=1713954052\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2478430/extras/24a814772cfd4c20d0e526867d920f75.webm?t=1713954052\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2478430/extras/24a814772cfd4c20d0e526867d920f75.mp4?t=1713954052\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Fly your way through 20 levels, divided in 5 different areas<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2478430/extras/67f389e9a20a192e860fe7398c7a8eb6.poster.avif?t=1713954052\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2478430/extras/67f389e9a20a192e860fe7398c7a8eb6.webm?t=1713954052\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2478430/extras/67f389e9a20a192e860fe7398c7a8eb6.mp4?t=1713954052\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Unlock new skins and use up to 12 different Special Attacks<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2478430/extras/b3cedb04359155b84ae9fb7ae122f618.poster.avif?t=1713954052\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2478430/extras/b3cedb04359155b84ae9fb7ae122f618.webm?t=1713954052\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2478430/extras/b3cedb04359155b84ae9fb7ae122f618.mp4?t=1713954052\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Collect powerups and become invincible<br><br>Play with a friend, and beat the game together!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2478430/extras/d886eb45ef46a746a3dfb17b794e054e.poster.avif?t=1713954052\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2478430/extras/d886eb45ef46a746a3dfb17b794e054e.webm?t=1713954052\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2478430/extras/d886eb45ef46a746a3dfb17b794e054e.mp4?t=1713954052\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>What are you waiting for? The world needs your help!<br><br>Let the battle begin!",
